Lookup "$(PointCloudLASClassifier_WORKSPACE_NAME)_AttributeValueMapper_LOOKUP_TABLE"   0               Created<comma><space>never<space>classified   1               Unclassified   2               Ground   3               Low<space>Vegetation   4               Medium<space>Vegetation   5               High<space>Vegetation   6               Building   7               Low<space>Point<space><openparen>noise<closeparen>   8               Model<space>Key-point<space><openparen>mass<space>point<closeparen>   9               Water   10              Reserved<space>for<space>ASPRS<space>Definition   11              Reserved<space>for<space>ASPRS<space>Definition   12              Overlap<space>Points   13              Reserved<space>for<space>ASPRS<space>Definition   ""              Reserved<space>for<space>ASPRS<space>Definition   ENCODED_SUPPORTUNICODE
